(firstQuint)Impact of Symbiotic Administration on Intestinal Function of Head and Neck Patients Surgically Treated.

 The study will be conducted offering the patients symbiotic product twice a day for seven days after the surgical treatment.

 Patients will be monitored for the number of stools, stools consistency, abdominal pain and gas overproduction.

